OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,FVeteran ITV Cymru Wales presenter,
OL,7,FAndrew Jones, has announced he is
OL,8,Fretiring after more than a quarter of
OL,9,Fa century at the company.
OL,11,FMr Jones joined ITV in the early
OL,12,F2000s, having spent much of his career
OL,13,Fin radio, lastly at Red Dragon FM. He
OL,14,Fquickly established himself as a
OL,15,Ftrusted voice, bringing the nation its
OL,16,Fbreakfast and lunchtime headlines as
OL,17,Fthe early morning presenter.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
