OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781803174
OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales has paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhim, saying his warmth and dedication
OL,8,Fto Welsh journalism has left an
OL,9,Findelible mark that will endure long
OL,10,Fafter he has stepped out of the studio.
OL,12,FAmongst colleagues, Andrew Jones'
OL,13,Fpassion for science and particularly
OL,14,FPhysics and Astronomy is well known,
OL,15,Feven at times sporting a tie with a
OL,16,Fpattern of the periodic table on it
OL,17,Fwhile presenting.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
