FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781803174
OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,FAudiences might not know but he is
OL,7,Falso a talented musician and once
OL,8,Fwrote the incidental music for two
OL,9,Fshows at the Edinburgh Fringe Festival.
OL,11,FHead of News and Programmes Zoe Thomas
OL,12,Fsaid: "For a generation, Andrew has
OL,13,Fbeen the familiar face of our early
OL,14,Fmorning news, and we are sure that
OL,15,Fviewers will miss his reassuring
OL,16,Fpresence and his trademark "Good
OL,17,FMorning."
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
