PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781803174
OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,F"After 25 distinguished years with ITV
OL,7,FCymru Wales, Andrew's immense
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and unwavering
OL,9,Freliability set a standard for the
OL,10,Fnewsroom. His contribution is
OL,11,Fimmeasurable, and he will be hard to
OL,12,Freplace.
OL,14,F"Beyond his professional life, Andrew
OL,15,Fwill be greatly missed as a valued
OL,16,Fcolleague and friend. We will miss his
OL,17,Fsense of humour and his huge wealth of
OL,18,Fknowledge, particularly his unrivalled
OL,19,Fknowledge of all things space related!
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
