FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781803174
OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,F"All his colleagues, past and present,
OL,7,Fextend their deepest thanks for his
OL,8,Fenormous contribution to ITV Cymru
OL,9,FWales and we wish him a long and happy
OL,10,Fretirement."
OL,12,FIn a statement, the long-serving
OL,13,Fpresenter said: "Over 25 years. More
OL,14,Fthan a quarter of a century. That's
OL,15,Fbeen my life at ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,17,F"A journey almost as long as the trek
OL,18,Ffrom the newsroom to the studio at
OL,19,FCulverhouse Cross!
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]uD@QOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
