PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781803174
OL,3,CWell-known ITV Cymru Wales presenter
OL,4,Cannounces his retirement after 25 years
OL,6,F"To everyone I've met; to all those
OL,7,FI've worked with; to everyone I've
OL,8,Finterviewed; to all those I've laughed
OL,9,Fand joked with and to those who kindly
OL,10,Fwatched: thank you.
OL,12,F"I'm on another journey now and those
OL,13,Fmemories walk with me."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@WO]
